title: Looking for bronze/silver, jgler and support to do ranked 5v's
body: Me and two friends are looking for a jg and support main to play with us as a 5 man premade for ranked, the 3 of us play daily and use skype to communicate, anyone whos interested add me on league, my use is StoleYaPenta
